My data directory is /Volume/Seagate\ Backup\ Disk/Ethereum.

To get a console:
  geth --datadir <my_datadir> console

At the console, to get my default account's balance:
  web3.fromWei(eth.getBalance(eth.coinbase), "ether")

To list accounts from the command line:
  geth --datadir <my_datadir> account list

